# Problem statement
--> Current internship search ecosystem is highly fragmented and inefficient 
    leading to information overload, missed opportunities, and decision fatique
--> Directly undermines progress towards SDG: 8 Decent Work and Economic Growth
--> Lack of integrated communication channel results in delayed or absent feedback 
    from employers. leaving applicants in a state of uncertainty.
--> Contributes  to emotional stress and reduced self-efficiacy among students, perpetuating
    inequities in access to decent work.
